title: Sonicare DiamondClean Pink Edition: whiter, healthier teeth for life | Philips | HX9362
description:
The new Philips Sonicare DiamondClean electric toothbrush Pink Edition makes your smile as brilliant
as you feel. It removes up to 100% more stains, and 7 times more plaque, than an manual toothbrush. 
Its award-winning design enables you to charge it by simply placing the toothbrush in its glass. 

Or, if you're on the move, its innovative charging case connects to your computer by USB. No matter where 
you go you'll always get a cleaner white, with pink.
